      ## Test plan

      This would be measured by the answer participants gave to task 4: <em>“Without tapping anything yet, what do you think the button “What’s nearby” does? Why?”</em>

      The participant needs to correctly identify that the “What’s nearby” button is for adding places to the map, <em><strong>before</strong> tapping on the button</em>.

